Package: RunningStats
Type: Package
Title: RunningStats
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-03-30
Authors@R: c(person("Simon", "Schoemaker", role = c("aut", "cre"),
  	     email = "simon.schoemaker@googlemail.com"),
	        person("Daniel", "Schumacher", role = c("aut"),
		     email = "daniel.schumacher@wwu.de"))
Maintainer: Simon Schoemaker <simon.schoemaker@googlemail.com>
Description: This package provides statistics for running tracks in the GPX-Format. It provides plot functions for maps and elevation profiles and accesses the OpenWeatherMap API for historical weather data.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0), trajectories, spacetime, OpenStreetMap, ggplot2, plotKML, signal, ggmap, rjson
